TAP-Formatter-Spreadsheet version 0.01
======================================

This Module provides Excel output with customizable formats for the 
Test::Harness output. This Module can be use for formatting the test
results along with creating bar charts or pie charts based on the output
results both for overall test summary and for individual tests.

This Module is based on TAP::Formatter::Console and TAP::Formatter::Base 
modules which are part of Core Perl distribution. TAP::Base is used as 
base class for this implementation. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Spreadsheet::WriteExcel TAP::Harness TAP::Base

